---+ Release 3.0.0u1

*Summary*: The CA Certificates have been updated for the IGTF 1.42 release.

*Release Date*: 13-Oct-2011

To be precise, we updated the following new RPMs to the production OSG yum repository:

%TABLE{ sort="off" valign="top" }%
| *Package* | *Replaces* |
| igtf-ca-certs-1.42-1 | igtf-ca-certs-1.41-1 |
| igtf-ca-certs-compat-1.42-1 | igtf-ca-certs-compat-1.41-1 |
| osg-ca-certs-1.24-1 | osg-ca-certs-1.23-1 |
| osg-ca-certs-compat-1.24-1 | osg-ca-certs-compat-1.24-1 |